        "channel_id": "4rn5g95hrj5w0xnsq107djy9we",
        "title": "Vision Pro momentum and platform updates",
        "body": "<h2>Vision Pro momentum and platform updates</h2>\n<p>The Vision Pro program continues to accelerate, with strong early developer engagement and platform growth. Apple has continued to expand the visionOS ecosystem with updates in version 2, targeting deeper spatial computing capabilities across iOS and macOS devices. The product line\u2019s launch, priced at $3,499, has sparked a global conversation about spatial technology, accessibility, and immersive experiences.</p>\n<p>Key signals include cross-device compatibility, developer tools improvements, and ongoing optimization of energy efficiency and on-device processing. Apple remains committed to privacy-preserving compute, balancing on-device intelligence with cloud-driven features where appropriate.</p>\n<p>For more context on the Vision Pro roadmap, read the parent press materials and internal strategy notes linked in the Newsroom.</p>\n<p>Read more in the internal Vision Pro updates and developer guides.</p>",
