        "title": "Apple Intelligence across ecosystems",
        "body": "<h2>Apple Intelligence across ecosystems</h2>\n<p>Apple Intelligence brings on-device privacy-preserving AI features to iPhone, iPad, and Mac, enabling smarter experiences while keeping user data on-device. This update highlights cross-platform integration, performance improvements, and privacy safeguards that minimize data leaving the device.</p>\n<p>The initiative spans iOS, iPadOS, and macOS, with new developer tools to help partners build privacy-conscious experiences. This aligns with Apple\u2019s privacy-first philosophy and the emphasis on on-device processing to protect user data.</p>\n<p>For deeper dives, consult the Vision Pro and hardware teams\u2019 notes on integration and privacy features.</p>\n<p>Read more in the internal briefs and security guidelines.</p>",
